messages.message:
Wanted to say awesome video for the soccer team. Only feedback. We should consider showing the document that was used to generate this data. It’s hard to follow how the data was rendered without seeing the document we were pulling the information from. @Bas 

https://instabase.com/blog/unveiling-the-promise-of-generative-ai/ (https://instabase.com/blog/unveiling-the-promise-of-generative-ai/)

Thanks @joshbronko ! Totally agree of course. We did not provide such specific instructions to the students (didn’t realize that was needed), and interestingly this was her choice to show it this way. For next university visits we’ll give more specific instructions!
I was impressed by the simple prompts she had to the results.
